CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 16, 1961, pg. A14, reads: "52nd Anniversary - Mr. and Mrs. Edward L. Johnson of Race St. celebrated their 52nd anniversary surrounded by family and friends. The pioneer Pittsburghers were married in 1909. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Edward L. Johnson and Mrs. Johnson cutting three tiered cake on their 52nd wedding anniversary, another version
